in the house.

36:25.776 --> 36:28.245
One was the young boy.

36:28.247 --> 36:31.347
And the other
is the lady of the house.

36:33.650 --> 36:35.785
You're the only lady
in the house.

36:35.787 --> 36:36.986
Mm-hmm.

36:36.988 --> 36:38.287
Oh, boy.

36:41.257 --> 36:43.391
What I got was that, you know,

36:43.393 --> 36:45.559
