37:32.791 --> 37:36.130
And she wants to get you
and then go after him.

37:39.103 --> 37:42.001
I feel sick right now.

37:51.450 --> 37:52.951
You don't look surprised.

37:52.953 --> 37:54.319
No.

37:54.321 --> 37:56.254
I know the whole family,

37:56.256 --> 37:59.022
and I saw what she did
to, basically, all of them.

38:08.868 --> 38:10.569
You okay?

38:10.571 --> 38:12.171
