when you were a kid?

38:20.445 --> 38:23.479
Oh, yeah. Absolutely.
Oh, absolutely.

38:25.249 --> 38:28.181
I'm just surprised
with Nathaniel.

38:29.883 --> 38:31.284
She was always like that.

38:31.286 --> 38:32.955
I mean,
does she really feel like

38:32.957 --> 38:35.293
