38:35.295 --> 38:38.163
Oh, yeah.
She had a hot temper, for sure.

38:41.334 --> 38:44.036
Well, I know this isn't
what you wanted to hear.

38:44.038 --> 38:47.642
I know it's something
I didn't want to hear, either.

38:47.644 --> 38:49.578
The big question left is,

38:49.580 --> 38:52.112
