unwanted visitors, so to speak.

39:05.759 --> 39:11.067
So, therefore, we kind of
want to put her to rest

39:11.069 --> 39:13.068
so that you're not going to
have to deal with her.

39:13.070 --> 39:16.838
Because my fear is that if
