39:16.840 --> 39:19.745
it's going to get worse.

39:19.747 --> 39:21.880
It could be so debilitating,

39:21.882 --> 39:25.351
I don't know
if you could get her out.

39:27.121 --> 39:29.655
My suggestion is

39:29.657 --> 39:32.761
to get an individual
that is a mental medium.

39:32.763 --> 39:37.030
A mental medium
is a type of medium

39:37.032 --> 39:42.534
that does not feel
the individual's death.

39:42.536 --> 39:48.169
Therefore, they won't be
as impacted by her.

39:48.171 --> 39:50.504
So, what is this mental medium
going to do?

39:50.506 --> 39:55.007
I would suggest
that they go in your backyard,

39:55.009 --> 39:58.340
