39:58.342 --> 40:01.478
What they're basically going to
be talking to her about

40:01.480 --> 40:05.985
is letting her
tell them her story

40:05.987 --> 40:09.352
to help her to move on.

40:09.354 --> 40:11.589
Will she leave at that point?

40:11.591 --> 40:13.091
Yes.

40:13.093 --> 40:16.459
So, it sounds like the biggest
problem here is your mom.

40:16.461 --> 40:18.593
Mm-hmm.

40:18.595 --> 40:21.801
As far as she's concerned,

40:21.803 --> 40:26.073
what I would suggest doing
is writing a letter to her.

40:26.075 --> 40:30.815
In this letter,
I would like you to focus

40:30.817 --> 40:33.619
on what she is no longer allowed
to do,

40:33.621 --> 40:36.222
that she is no longer allowed

40:36.224 --> 40:41.466
to control you, your home,
your family, or your dreams,

40:41.468 --> 40:46.773
that you are taking back
the power and control

40:46.775 --> 40:49.142
of your home and your family.

40:49.144 --> 40:52.145
And then,
have a physical medium,

40:52.147 --> 40:55.945
which is somebody like me,
come to the home.

40:55.947 --> 40:59.649
And you and this physical medium
are going to deal with her.

40:59.651 --> 41:04.051
Then, you're going to
read your letter.

41:04.053 --> 41:05.787
I want you to yell.
I do.

41:05.789 --> 41:08.388
I feel like you need to
fricking yell at her.

41:08.390 --> 41:11.657
Don't let her stop you.

41:11.659 --> 41:13.358
I don't care whether you feel
like you're going to throw up.

41:13.360 --> 41:14.659
I don't care
if you do throw up.

41:14.661 --> 41:17.997
I don't care what happens

41:17.999 --> 41:22.169
as long as you finish
what you write.

41:22.171 --> 41:24.406
Right.
Once you're done,

41:24.408 --> 41:29.510
then you tell that physical
medium, "Get rid of her."

41:32.915 --> 41:35.416
Are you afraid to do this?

41:36.685 --> 41:38.586
