41:38.588 --> 41:41.324
Once I get started,
I'll be on a roll.

41:42.427 --> 41:44.495
I see how protective you are
of him.

41:44.497 --> 41:46.129
Yes. I am very much.

41:46.131 --> 41:48.699
What about you? Are you
going to take Amy's advice?

41:48.701 --> 41:50.935
Yes, definitely.

41:50.937 --> 41:52.770
I look forward to it.

41:52.772 --> 41:55.640
Cynthia has her work
cut out for her.

41:55.642 --> 41:59.175
But I believe if she's able
to stand up to her mother,

41:59.177 --> 42:02.246
